Tyler Kost, 19, was arrested last May for sexual crimes against 13 girls between 13 and 17 years old, most of whom were former classmates at Poston Butte High School .
The Pinal County Attorney's Office says there is a 'treasure trove' of evidence proving the girls lied about sexual abuse .
Kost faces 30 charges in three indictments ranging from sexual abuse to child molestation .